Vikunja Task Hub

This project began as a derivative of vikunja-homeassistant:
https://github.com/joeShuff/vikunja-homeassistant

The derivative has been substantially modified, including replacement of the
entity/device model with a direct dashboard API and custom card, new project and
category management, bulk task actions, rich task editing, attachment support,
responsive layout work, and revised configuration and documentation.

